---
title: Chicken Sausage & Pepper Heroes with Melty Mozzarella & Garlic Potato Wedges
description: For these Little Italy–inspired sandwiches, our chefs have pulled out all the stops. Mini baguette loaves are split open and slathered with garlic butter, then toasted until crispy and golden. They’re stuffed with crumbled pork sausage and tender, sautéed onions and peppers, then blanketed with mozzarella and baked again to ooey-gooey perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6372b5ee081787c4b902394e-e1fd88f3.jpg
